### Transition Scenes

#### 9. MergeScene (`src/game/MergeScene.cpp`)

**Purpose**: Literal door-through transition between gotchi and story modes

**Dimensions**: 720×720 pixels

**Visuals**:
- Standalone scene with no background art
- Uses `PortalEffect` (same as OfficeScene's portal)
- Clear color fades black ↔ white

**Modes**:
- `MERGE_IN`: Camera starts far (10), pushes to near (0.1), color black→white
- `MERGE_OUT`: Camera starts near (0.1), pulls to far (10), color white→black

**Duration**: 7 seconds (configurable via `MERGE_DURATION`)

**Controls**:
- Tab key toggles direction mid-transition (debug)

---

### Menu/Utility Scenes

#### 10. TitleScene (`src/game/TitleScene.cpp`)

**Purpose**: Main menu with save system

**Dimensions**: 720×720 pixels

**UI**:
- "NEW GAME" button - creates default GameState, saves to slot 0
- "LOAD GAME" button - shows slot selection UI
- "SAVE" button (main menu) - saves current GameState to active slot

**Save Slots**:
- 3 slot buttons with summary display (playtime, beat index)
- SAVE/DELETE/BACK action buttons (shown when "Load Game" selected)

**Navigation**:
- Press 9 to return to title from any scene
- Transitions to `GotchiScene` after new/load

**Background**: Solid black

