## Input System

### SceneInputHandler (`src/engine/SceneInputHandler.hpp/.cpp`)

**Action Mappings**:

```cpp
"move_left"    → KEY_A
"move_right"   → KEY_D
"move_up"      → KEY_W
"move_down"    → KEY_S
"jump"         → KEY_SPACE
"interact"     → KEY_E
"pause"        → KEY_P
"accept"       → KEY_ENTER
"cancel"       → KEY_ESCAPE
```

**Input States**:
- Pressed (P) - Single frame on key down
- Held (H) - Every frame while key is down
- Released (R) - Single frame on key up

### Input in Scenes

```cpp
// Check action state
if (ih->isActionPressed("jump")) {
    // Jump logic
}

// Get raw key state
if (ih->isKeyHeld(KEY_LEFT_SHIFT)) {
    // Sprint logic
}

// Get mouse position
Vector2 mouseWorld = ih->getMouseWorldPosition();
```

### Key Bindings (Keyboard)

| Key | Scene | Function |
|-----|-------|----------|
| 3 | Any | Switch to InputTestScene |
| 4 | Any | Switch to SpriteTestScene |
| 5 | Any | Switch to HexViewScene |
| 7 | Any | Switch to SceneSelectScene |
| 9 | Any | Switch to TitleScene |
| E | Pizza Parlor/Apartment/Therapist/Office/School | Trigger next story event |
| TAB | MergeScene | Toggle merge direction (debug) |
| ESC | All | Exit game |

---

## Asset System

### AssetPack (`src/engine/AssetPack.hpp/.cpp`)

**Format**: `assets.rres` - Packed resource file

**Loading Patterns**:

```cpp
// Single texture
Texture2D tex = AssetPack::loadTexture("gotchis/001/idle_00.png");

// Multiple frames (numbered sequence)
std::vector<Texture2D> frames = AssetPack::loadFrames("gotchis/001", "idle");

// Unload
AssetPack::unloadFrames(frames);
```

**Asset Keys** (relative to assets.rres root):
- `"gotchis/001/idle_00.png"`
- `"gotchis/001/walk_00.png"`
- `"ui/buttons/menu_button.png"`

---

## Scene Flow Architecture

### Scene Transitions

The game uses a **state machine** for scene transitions:

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                            Scene Flow                                   │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                         │
│  ┌─────────┐                                                            │
│  │ Title   │                                                            │
│  │ Scene   │                                                            │
│  └────┬────┘                                                            │
│       │                                                                                 │
│       ▼                                                                                 │
│  ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────────┐                                                        │
│  │  New     │  │   Load       │                                                        │
│  │  Game    │  │   Game       │                                                        │
│  └────┬─────┘  └─────┬────────┘                                                        │
│       │              │                                                                 │
│       └───────┬──────┘                                                                 │
│               ▼                                                                        │
│  ┌───────────────┐  ┌────────────┐                                                     │
│  │  Load From     │  │  Save To   │                                                     │
│  │  Slot 0/1/2    │  │  Slot      │                                                     │
│  └───────┬───────┘  └─────┬───────┘                                                     │
│          │                │                                                            │
│          └────────┬───────┘                                                            │
│                   ▼                                                                    │
│  ┌───────────────────────────────┐                                                     │
│  │        ┌────────┐             │                                                     │
│  │        │Gotchi  │◄────────────┘                                                     │
│  │        │Scene   │                                                                   │
│  │        └────┬───┘                                                                   │
│  │             │                                                                       │
│  │  Merge Button (MergeRequested)                                                     │
│  │             │                                                                       │
│  │             ▼                                                                       │
│  │        ┌────────┐                                                                   │
│  │        │Merge   │                                                                   │
│  │        │Scene   │                                                                   │
│  │        └───┬────┘                                                                   │
│  │            │                                                                        │
│  │            ▼                                                                        │
│  │      ┌──────────────┐                                                               │
│  │      │ Story        │                                                               │
│  │      │ Sequencer    │                                                               │
│  │      │ (Box D)      │                                                               │
│  │      └──────┬───────┘                                                               │
│  │             │                                                                        │
│  │  ┌──────────┴────────────────────────────────┐                                       │
│  │  │                                           │                                       │
│  │  ▼                                           ▼                                       │
│  │ Pizza Parlor   Apartment   Office   School   Therapist                             │
│  │     │              │            │       │           │                                │
│  │     └──────────────┴────────────┴───────┴───────────┘                                │
│  │             │                                                                        │
